            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華新(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1605-TW</a>)15日12:01股價上漲2.9元，報43.8元，漲幅7.09%，成交264,683張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華新(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1605-TW</a>)所屬產業為電器電纜，主要業務為電線電纜、鋼線鋼纜及特殊鋼之生產與銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲3.15%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1.66%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+994 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-20,314 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+24,544 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-3,236 張</li> <li>融資增減：+9,294 張</li> <li>融券增減：-641 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
